                  ],
                  "url": [
                    "https://theexperimentpublishing.com/catalogs/spring-2021/the-lost-art-of-doing-nothing/"
                  ],
                  "summary": [
                    {
                      "html": "Don‚Äôt you think it‚Äôs time for a break? Plagued‚Äîas we are!‚Äîby nonstop pings and notifications, we have lost the knack of zoning out. Kicking back. Slacking off. Even when pandemic-induced lockdowns forcibly cleared our calendars, many who thought I‚Äôm free! filled their days with Netflix and doomscrolling. How can we reclaim our free time (planned or not) to truly rest and reset?",
                      "value": "Don‚Äôt you think it‚Äôs time for a break? Plagued‚Äîas we are!‚Äîby nonstop pings and notifications, we have lost the knack of zoning out. Kicking back. Slacking off. Even when pandemic-induced lockdowns forcibly cleared our calendars, many who thought I‚Äôm free! filled their days with Netflix and doomscrolling. How can we reclaim our free time (planned or not) to truly rest and reset?"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "value": "https://theexperimentpublishing.com/catalogs/spring-2021/the-lost-art-of-doing-nothing/"
